divs: Sighting Detailsthe ufo appeared to be between 1500 and 5000 feet in the air. it was round with a black main body with one white light at one point of the disk and another of the same color at the opposite side. the object was moving quietly from southeast to northwest and the lights were moving around the object in a counter-clockwise direction as observed from below.
Summary: Black, round, with two visible lights on opposite ends of the solid round object.
